  ('27c3229e-f107-490d-b8c2-7e417ae64456-ex1', '27c3229e-f107-490d-b8c2-7e417ae64456', 'labor', 'The job requires hard physical labor.', '这份工作需要繁重的体力劳动。'),
  ('27c3229e-f107-490d-b8c2-7e417ae64456-ex2', '27c3229e-f107-490d-b8c2-7e417ae64456', 'labor', 'The accord strengthens labor protections throughout the regional supply chain.', '该协定加强了整个区域供应链的劳工保护。'),
  ('de87fe04-351e-415d-a1bd-77dae3609465-ex1', 'de87fe04-351e-415d-a1bd-77dae3609465', 'refer', 'Please refer to page ten for details.', '详情请参阅第十页。'),
  ('de87fe04-351e-415d-a1bd-77dae3609465-ex2', 'de87fe04-351e-415d-a1bd-77dae3609465', 'refer', 'The panel resolved to refer the matter to the enforcement division for formal action.', '专家组决定将此事移交执法部门正式处理。'),
  ('5f4e3a04-5cac-42fe-a328-c7926318cfd6-ex1', '5f4e3a04-5cac-42fe-a328-c7926318cfd6', 'concept', 'The concept of the game is simple.', '这个游戏的概念很简单。'),
  ('5f4e3a04-5cac-42fe-a328-c7926318cfd6-ex2', '5f4e3a04-5cac-42fe-a328-c7926318cfd6', 'concept', 'The ruling refines the concept of proximate causation in environmental liability.', '该裁决细化了环境责任中近因的概念。'),
  ('0006a8b3-78cc-4e46-ab94-82bcea53361c-ex1', '0006a8b3-78cc-4e46-ab94-82bcea53361c', 'client', 'The lawyer met with her client.', '律师会见了她的客户。'),
