  ('f7df09e5-6d2b-4b78-98d1-e175f8cfd4c5-ex1', 'f7df09e5-6d2b-4b78-98d1-e175f8cfd4c5', 'nine', 'The store opens at nine.', '商店九点开门。'),
  ('f7df09e5-6d2b-4b78-98d1-e175f8cfd4c5-ex2', 'f7df09e5-6d2b-4b78-98d1-e175f8cfd4c5', 'nine', 'All nine justices concurred in the judgment, though their reasoning diverged.', '九位大法官一致同意判决结果，尽管推理各不相同。'),
