  ('bb3de8db-411c-420d-a93f-2248a9245928-ex2', 'bb3de8db-411c-420d-a93f-2248a9245928', 'conduct', 'The inquiry will conduct hearings into alleged misconduct at the highest levels.', '调查组将就最高层涉嫌的不当行为举行听证。'),
  ('3ae481d5-6331-41a8-bff5-26c10800bef6-ex1', '3ae481d5-6331-41a8-bff5-26c10800bef6', 'announce', 'They will announce the winners tonight.', '他们今晚将公布获奖者。'),
  ('3ae481d5-6331-41a8-bff5-26c10800bef6-ex2', '3ae481d5-6331-41a8-bff5-26c10800bef6', 'announce', 'The central bank declined to announce a timetable for unwinding its asset purchases.', '央行拒绝公布缩减资产购买的时间表。'),
  ('54897660-d191-4a08-b30f-cd062ef72813-ex1', '54897660-d191-4a08-b30f-cd062ef72813', 'conversation', 'We had a nice conversation over coffee.', '我们边喝咖啡边愉快地聊天。'),
  ('54897660-d191-4a08-b30f-cd062ef72813-ex2', '54897660-d191-4a08-b30f-cd062ef72813', 'conversation', 'The intercepted conversations formed the evidentiary core of the prosecution''s case.', '被截获的谈话构成了控方案件的核心证据。'),
  ('f6ddd312-5a35-4988-903e-f3f38805a9d7-ex1', 'f6ddd312-5a35-4988-903e-f3f38805a9d7', 'examine', 'The doctor will examine you now.', '医生现在给你检查。'),
  ('f6ddd312-5a35-4988-903e-f3f38805a9d7-ex2', 'f6ddd312-5a35-4988-903e-f3f38805a9d7', 'examine', 'The committee will examine whether the existing safeguards remain fit for purpose.', '委员会将审查现有保障措施是否仍然适用。'),
