  ('6c81861d-509c-4fad-91d9-7b6720ef458d-ex1', '6c81861d-509c-4fad-91d9-7b6720ef458d', 'attend', 'Will you attend the meeting tomorrow?', '你明天参加会议吗？'),
  ('6c81861d-509c-4fad-91d9-7b6720ef458d-ex2', '6c81861d-509c-4fad-91d9-7b6720ef458d', 'attend', 'Delegates from forty jurisdictions will attend the convention''s review conference.', '来自四十个司法管辖区的代表将出席公约审议大会。'),
  ('7ba65c2f-bbd7-44c5-840e-b469b3d378de-ex1', '7ba65c2f-bbd7-44c5-840e-b469b3d378de', 'completely', 'I completely forgot about the meeting.', '我把会议的事忘得一干二净。'),
  ('7ba65c2f-bbd7-44c5-840e-b469b3d378de-ex2', '7ba65c2f-bbd7-44c5-840e-b469b3d378de', 'completely', 'The legacy system was completely decommissioned following the phased migration.', '在分阶段迁移完成后，旧系统被彻底停用。'),
  ('eda53346-0a5d-4c14-9f7c-6f2725ef1dad-ex1', 'eda53346-0a5d-4c14-9f7c-6f2725ef1dad', 'variety', 'The market sells a variety of fruits.', '市场上出售各种各样的水果。'),
  ('eda53346-0a5d-4c14-9f7c-6f2725ef1dad-ex2', 'eda53346-0a5d-4c14-9f7c-6f2725ef1dad', 'variety', 'The portfolio encompasses a variety of instruments calibrated to distinct risk appetites.', '该投资组合涵盖针对不同风险偏好配置的多种工具。'),
