  ('909dc6a1-c5b5-4ccb-8a41-4d58146f6bfc-ex2', '909dc6a1-c5b5-4ccb-8a41-4d58146f6bfc', 'investigation', 'The investigation uncovered a coordinated scheme spanning multiple subsidiaries.', '调查揭露了一个横跨多家子公司的协同舞弊方案。'),
