  ('36d1b41a-33e2-4041-a9e2-8d99feeb1282-ex1', '36d1b41a-33e2-4041-a9e2-8d99feeb1282', 'conflict', 'The two friends had a small conflict.', '这两个朋友之间有点小矛盾。'),
