  ('f69ed9da-3992-4268-9bcd-5facc81c579c-ex1', 'f69ed9da-3992-4268-9bcd-5facc81c579c', 'argument', 'They had an argument about money.', '他们为钱争吵了一番。'),
  ('f69ed9da-3992-4268-9bcd-5facc81c579c-ex2', 'f69ed9da-3992-4268-9bcd-5facc81c579c', 'argument', 'The appellate court found the constitutional argument unpersuasive on the record presented.', '上诉法院认为，就所提交的案卷而言，这一宪法论点缺乏说服力。'),
