  ('9ae584a2-b058-4090-ac87-5a5bc29a7018-ex2', '9ae584a2-b058-4090-ac87-5a5bc29a7018', 'camp', 'Conditions in the displacement camps deteriorated as humanitarian access was curtailed.', '随着人道主义通道受限，安置营地的条件不断恶化。'),
