  ('c312da43-cbe5-409b-a198-9e4af866297d-ex1', 'c312da43-cbe5-409b-a198-9e4af866297d', 'somehow', 'We will get there somehow.', '我们总会想办法到那里的。'),
  ('c312da43-cbe5-409b-a198-9e4af866297d-ex2', 'c312da43-cbe5-409b-a198-9e4af866297d', 'somehow', 'The transfers somehow eluded every layer of the compliance apparatus.', '这些转账竟然躲过了合规体系的每一道防线。'),
  ('dfeed65c-1d0e-4ba8-abad-93a14396fc44-ex1', 'dfeed65c-1d0e-4ba8-abad-93a14396fc44', 'organize', 'Let''s organize the books by subject.', '我们把书按学科整理一下吧。'),
  ('dfeed65c-1d0e-4ba8-abad-93a14396fc44-ex2', 'dfeed65c-1d0e-4ba8-abad-93a14396fc44', 'organize', 'The statute protects the right of workers to organize without employer interference.', '该法规保护劳动者不受雇主干预组建工会的权利。'),
