  ('e9ae2fd0-8bf4-4c83-98ec-58e60abd60f2-ex1', 'e9ae2fd0-8bf4-4c83-98ec-58e60abd60f2', 'union', 'The workers joined the union.', '工人们加入了工会。'),
  ('e9ae2fd0-8bf4-4c83-98ec-58e60abd60f2-ex2', 'e9ae2fd0-8bf4-4c83-98ec-58e60abd60f2', 'union', 'The customs union eliminates internal tariffs while harmonizing external schedules.', '关税同盟取消内部关税，同时统一对外税率表。'),
  ('37685c0b-992d-4aeb-a036-6e85eb493ef5-ex1', '37685c0b-992d-4aeb-a036-6e85eb493ef5', 'desk', 'My desk is covered with papers.', '我的书桌上堆满了文件。'),
  ('37685c0b-992d-4aeb-a036-6e85eb493ef5-ex2', '37685c0b-992d-4aeb-a036-6e85eb493ef5', 'desk', 'Every claim passes through a single adjudication desk to ensure consistency.', '所有索赔均经由单一裁定窗口处理，以确保一致性。'),
