  ('2c7ccfee-9f29-4db7-b799-b92876430f4d-ex2', '2c7ccfee-9f29-4db7-b799-b92876430f4d', 'thanks', 'The recovery owes much, thanks largely to coordinated fiscal intervention.', '这次复苏在很大程度上要归功于协调一致的财政干预。'),
  ('f352ce6c-8cc9-4a9d-89d5-4899b7221416-ex1', 'f352ce6c-8cc9-4a9d-89d5-4899b7221416', 'fruit', 'Eat more fruit and vegetables.', '多吃水果和蔬菜。'),
  ('f352ce6c-8cc9-4a9d-89d5-4899b7221416-ex2', 'f352ce6c-8cc9-4a9d-89d5-4899b7221416', 'fruit', 'The negotiations bore fruit only after both parties softened entrenched positions.', '双方软化强硬立场之后，谈判才取得成果。'),
