  ('a44f98a4-4735-459b-9de5-d64d30988d06-ex2', 'a44f98a4-4735-459b-9de5-d64d30988d06', 'expensive', 'Delayed remediation proved far more expensive than timely compliance would have been.', '事实证明，延迟整改的代价远高于及时合规。'),
  ('86cfb3ac-b5a9-480e-80a0-953fc2e7a392-ex1', '86cfb3ac-b5a9-480e-80a0-953fc2e7a392', 'yellow', 'She painted the kitchen yellow.', '她把厨房刷成了黄色。'),
