  ('e839c4ec-23c2-4a8f-8087-483ac24cc119-ex2', 'e839c4ec-23c2-4a8f-8087-483ac24cc119', 'conclusion', 'The panel''s conclusion rests on evidence corroborated across independent sources.', '专家组的结论建立在经多个独立来源印证的证据之上。'),
  ('223e507d-6efc-4bcb-aa03-9035bcda6338-ex1', '223e507d-6efc-4bcb-aa03-9035bcda6338', 'prime', 'The prime minister gave a speech today.', '总理今天发表了讲话。'),
  ('223e507d-6efc-4bcb-aa03-9035bcda6338-ex2', '223e507d-6efc-4bcb-aa03-9035bcda6338', 'prime', 'Maintaining price stability remains the prime mandate of the central bank.', '维护物价稳定仍是中央银行的首要职责。'),
  ('19edbf2a-7c15-4c59-affd-85ed8332199d-ex1', '19edbf2a-7c15-4c59-affd-85ed8332199d', 'shadow', 'The tree casts a long shadow.', '那棵树投下长长的影子。'),
  ('19edbf2a-7c15-4c59-affd-85ed8332199d-ex2', '19edbf2a-7c15-4c59-affd-85ed8332199d', 'shadow', 'The shadow banking sector operates largely beyond prudential supervision.', '影子银行部门大体游离于审慎监管之外。'),
