  ('381b28ff-9ec0-4b4f-a491-e18beddeb009-ex1', '381b28ff-9ec0-4b4f-a491-e18beddeb009', 'dance', 'They danced all night at the wedding.', '他们在婚礼上跳了一整晚的舞。'),
  ('381b28ff-9ec0-4b4f-a491-e18beddeb009-ex2', '381b28ff-9ec0-4b4f-a491-e18beddeb009', 'dance', 'The negotiations resembled an intricate diplomatic dance of concession and restraint.', '这场谈判宛如一场让步与克制交织的复杂外交博弈。'),
