  ('32b7d180-7435-4410-885d-e9818734b4e8-ex2', '32b7d180-7435-4410-885d-e9818734b4e8', 'regulation', 'The regulation imposes binding obligations directly applicable in all member states.', '该条例规定的约束性义务在所有成员国直接适用。'),
  ('e00c65b5-25dc-4e55-8546-c03f44cd7caa-ex1', 'e00c65b5-25dc-4e55-8546-c03f44cd7caa', 'being', 'Every human being deserves respect.', '每个人都应受到尊重。'),
  ('e00c65b5-25dc-4e55-8546-c03f44cd7caa-ex2', 'e00c65b5-25dc-4e55-8546-c03f44cd7caa', 'being', 'The arrangement came into being through decades of incremental institutional accretion.', '这一安排是数十年制度逐步累积演化而成的。'),
  ('3e09b709-b749-49bf-874c-c95f81dc2657-ex1', '3e09b709-b749-49bf-874c-c95f81dc2657', 'ring', 'She wears a silver ring.', '她戴着一枚银戒指。'),
