  ('1c4b2374-4241-400a-a506-8dd324bcd5e0-ex1', '1c4b2374-4241-400a-a506-8dd324bcd5e0', 'largely', 'The success was largely due to teamwork.', '这次成功主要归功于团队合作。'),
  ('1c4b2374-4241-400a-a506-8dd324bcd5e0-ex2', '1c4b2374-4241-400a-a506-8dd324bcd5e0', 'largely', 'The reforms remain largely unimplemented despite repeated legislative mandates.', '尽管立法机构一再授权，这些改革大多仍未落实。'),
  ('92d7074c-a340-4d00-a75e-bb93789e91c3-ex1', '92d7074c-a340-4d00-a75e-bb93789e91c3', 'shift', 'She works the night shift this week.', '她这周上夜班。'),
  ('92d7074c-a340-4d00-a75e-bb93789e91c3-ex2', '92d7074c-a340-4d00-a75e-bb93789e91c3', 'shift', 'The ruling marks a decisive shift in the allocation of evidentiary burdens.', '该裁决标志着举证责任分配的决定性转变。'),
