  ('a72dee83-9a39-4442-9813-222ab6ccf0ce-ex2', 'a72dee83-9a39-4442-9813-222ab6ccf0ce', 'mark', 'The accord marks the culmination of a decade of incremental confidence-building.', '该协定是十年渐进式建立信任努力的巅峰成果。'),
  ('f469cab5-1cf1-4559-8dfb-09b87376d012-ex1', 'f469cab5-1cf1-4559-8dfb-09b87376d012', 'locate', 'Can you locate the museum on this map?', '你能在这张地图上找到博物馆吗？'),
  ('f469cab5-1cf1-4559-8dfb-09b87376d012-ex2', 'f469cab5-1cf1-4559-8dfb-09b87376d012', 'locate', 'Investigators failed to locate assets corresponding to the declared holdings.', '调查人员未能找到与申报持有量对应的资产。'),
  ('f02e7839-2637-42a2-9809-31b7959ca9d2-ex1', 'f02e7839-2637-42a2-9809-31b7959ca9d2', 'county', 'The county fair is this weekend.', '县集市这个周末举行。'),
  ('f02e7839-2637-42a2-9809-31b7959ca9d2-ex2', 'f02e7839-2637-42a2-9809-31b7959ca9d2', 'county', 'Each county administers the program subject to uniform state oversight.', '各县在州统一监督下实施该项目。'),
  ('808d656d-22c1-4b0e-a978-a78a344ee5a7-ex1', '808d656d-22c1-4b0e-a978-a78a344ee5a7', 'appearance', 'He made a brief appearance at the party.', '他在聚会上短暂露面。'),
  ('808d656d-22c1-4b0e-a978-a78a344ee5a7-ex2', '808d656d-22c1-4b0e-a978-a78a344ee5a7', 'appearance', 'Adjudicators must avoid even the appearance of partiality toward either party.', '裁判者必须避免对任何一方表现出哪怕表面上的偏袒。'),
  ('2874dbc5-20c4-4ee4-aaba-b89df57ca30c-ex1', '2874dbc5-20c4-4ee4-aaba-b89df57ca30c', 'package', 'A package arrived for you this morning.', '今天早上有你的一个包裹。'),
  ('2874dbc5-20c4-4ee4-aaba-b89df57ca30c-ex2', '2874dbc5-20c4-4ee4-aaba-b89df57ca30c', 'package', 'The stimulus package channels funds through audited municipal programs.', '经济刺激方案通过经审计的市政项目划拨资金。'),
  ('e35b9cab-0618-47ba-ac5a-8079e6f4e144-ex1', 'e35b9cab-0618-47ba-ac5a-8079e6f4e144', 'difficulty', 'She has difficulty hearing in noisy places.', '在嘈杂的地方她听不清。'),
  ('e35b9cab-0618-47ba-ac5a-8079e6f4e144-ex2', 'e35b9cab-0618-47ba-ac5a-8079e6f4e144', 'difficulty', 'The principal difficulty lies in verifying compliance without intrusive inspection.', '主要困难在于如何在不进行侵入式核查的情况下验证履约。'),
  ('757adb9a-d553-4768-9ece-381d421f30f8-ex1', '757adb9a-d553-4768-9ece-381d421f30f8', 'bridge', 'We walked across the old bridge.', '我们走过那座老桥。'),
  ('757adb9a-d553-4768-9ece-381d421f30f8-ex2', '757adb9a-d553-4768-9ece-381d421f30f8', 'bridge', 'The interim facility serves as a bridge pending the permanent financing arrangement.', '这笔过渡性融资在永久融资安排落实之前发挥衔接作用。'),
  ('997ab877-8cf8-455e-8043-751c299c155b-ex1', '997ab877-8cf8-455e-8043-751c299c155b', 'recommend', 'Can you recommend a good restaurant?', '你能推荐一家好餐厅吗？'),
  ('997ab877-8cf8-455e-8043-751c299c155b-ex2', '997ab877-8cf8-455e-8043-751c299c155b', 'recommend', 'The commission will recommend statutory amendments to close the identified loopholes.', '委员会将建议修订法规，以堵塞已发现的漏洞。'),
  ('f465e1c0-43fb-4401-bdcd-e0974067a182-ex1', 'f465e1c0-43fb-4401-bdcd-e0974067a182', 'obvious', 'The answer is obvious to everyone.', '答案对每个人来说都显而易见。'),
  ('f465e1c0-43fb-4401-bdcd-e0974067a182-ex2', 'f465e1c0-43fb-4401-bdcd-e0974067a182', 'obvious', 'The conflict of interest was obvious yet remained undisclosed for years.', '这一利益冲突显而易见，却多年未予披露。'),
  ('7be729fc-2981-452b-b3bf-8a1635026c1e-ex1', '7be729fc-2981-452b-b3bf-8a1635026c1e', 'basically', 'Basically, we just need more time.', '基本上，我们只是需要更多时间。'),
  ('7be729fc-2981-452b-b3bf-8a1635026c1e-ex2', '7be729fc-2981-452b-b3bf-8a1635026c1e', 'basically', 'The defense argued that the charges basically duplicate claims already adjudicated.', '辩方认为，这些指控实质上重复了已经审结的诉求。'),
  ('67876dbf-18c5-4cfb-96be-1e025eb9ac6f-ex1', '67876dbf-18c5-4cfb-96be-1e025eb9ac6f', 'e-mail', 'Send me an e-mail when you arrive.', '你到了给我发封邮件。'),
  ('67876dbf-18c5-4cfb-96be-1e025eb9ac6f-ex2', '67876dbf-18c5-4cfb-96be-1e025eb9ac6f', 'e-mail', 'The subpoenaed e-mails documented contemporaneous awareness of the defect.', '被传调的电子邮件证明当时各方对缺陷已经知情。'),
  ('275e2819-ea06-4943-a147-7a52f5d99119-ex1', '275e2819-ea06-4943-a147-7a52f5d99119', 'generate', 'The dam generates electricity for the city.', '大坝为城市发电。'),
