  ('71ffcc73-44c8-4553-8588-eede542be453-ex2', '71ffcc73-44c8-4553-8588-eede542be453', 'bowl', 'The stadium bowl was re-engineered to satisfy revised seismic standards.', '体育场碗状看台经过重新设计，以满足修订后的抗震标准。'),
  ('cbe49675-3061-42a6-89a4-8870868416e8-ex1', 'cbe49675-3061-42a6-89a4-8870868416e8', 'equal', 'Cut the cake into equal pieces.', '把蛋糕切成大小相等的几块。'),
  ('cbe49675-3061-42a6-89a4-8870868416e8-ex2', 'cbe49675-3061-42a6-89a4-8870868416e8', 'equal', 'The charter guarantees equal protection irrespective of origin or status.', '宪章保障人人享有平等保护，不论出身或地位。'),
  ('ec95bbbb-e647-4774-9529-3c22932b01cd-ex1', 'ec95bbbb-e647-4774-9529-3c22932b01cd', 'forth', 'The ducks swam back and forth.', '鸭子游来游去。'),
  ('ec95bbbb-e647-4774-9529-3c22932b01cd-ex2', 'ec95bbbb-e647-4774-9529-3c22932b01cd', 'forth', 'The white paper sets forth the principles governing the forthcoming legislation.', '白皮书阐明了即将出台立法所遵循的原则。'),
  ('2336724d-77b6-42de-b0d5-cd9da9f4c668-ex1', '2336724d-77b6-42de-b0d5-cd9da9f4c668', 'frame', 'I bought a frame for the photo.', '我给照片买了个相框。'),
