  ('365f9590-ccb6-4191-a196-1ca17b67dcc1-ex1', '365f9590-ccb6-4191-a196-1ca17b67dcc1', 'conservative', 'He wears conservative dark suits.', '他穿着保守的深色西装。'),
  ('365f9590-ccb6-4191-a196-1ca17b67dcc1-ex2', '365f9590-ccb6-4191-a196-1ca17b67dcc1', 'conservative', 'Even conservative projections imply funding shortfalls within the decade.', '即使是保守的预测也意味着十年内将出现资金缺口。'),
  ('e080dc96-98e1-497b-9cf7-ba3515bd46d5-ex1', 'e080dc96-98e1-497b-9cf7-ba3515bd46d5', 'eliminate', 'We eliminated several wrong answers.', '我们排除了几个错误答案。'),
  ('e080dc96-98e1-497b-9cf7-ba3515bd46d5-ex2', 'e080dc96-98e1-497b-9cf7-ba3515bd46d5', 'eliminate', 'The accord aims to eliminate tariff barriers across substantially all trade.', '该协定旨在消除几乎所有贸易领域的关税壁垒。'),
