  ('19706407-de1a-48bc-bc21-dd0a8a972a72-ex1', '19706407-de1a-48bc-bc21-dd0a8a972a72', 'hall', 'The concert hall was full.', '音乐厅座无虚席。'),
  ('19706407-de1a-48bc-bc21-dd0a8a972a72-ex2', '19706407-de1a-48bc-bc21-dd0a8a972a72', 'hall', 'The city hall hearings drew submissions from hundreds of affected residents.', '市政厅听证会收到了数百名受影响居民的意见。'),
  ('b04a0ba5-0067-45c9-805b-5cc5a766dac2-ex1', 'b04a0ba5-0067-45c9-805b-5cc5a766dac2', 'trust', 'I trust you completely.', '我完全信任你。'),
