  ('9b28fafa-2a22-4c4d-ad23-72a8a603ea96-ex1', '9b28fafa-2a22-4c4d-ad23-72a8a603ea96', 'ocean', 'We watched the sunset over the ocean.', '我们看着太阳落入海面。'),
