  ('4324ae26-43c9-458e-9088-80962de46656-ex1', '4324ae26-43c9-458e-9088-80962de46656', 'meanwhile', 'Meanwhile, dinner was getting cold.', '与此同时，晚饭渐渐凉了。'),
