  ('751b4c1f-f418-4587-ae58-98ffd154793f-ex2', '751b4c1f-f418-4587-ae58-98ffd154793f', 'division', 'The division of competences between levels of government remains contested.', '各级政府之间的权限划分仍存争议。'),
  ('e1f4ae71-e040-4343-bb71-ade77bc54395-ex1', 'e1f4ae71-e040-4343-bb71-ade77bc54395', 'confirm', 'Please confirm your reservation by phone.', '请电话确认您的预订。'),
  ('e1f4ae71-e040-4343-bb71-ade77bc54395-ex2', 'e1f4ae71-e040-4343-bb71-ade77bc54395', 'confirm', 'Independent laboratories confirmed the findings under blinded protocols.', '独立实验室在盲测方案下证实了这些发现。'),
