  ('c9f46ce0-2938-49da-9f76-b0facfcd8558-ex2', 'c9f46ce0-2938-49da-9f76-b0facfcd8558', 'talent', 'The retention of specialized talent has become a strategic regulatory concern.', '专业人才的留任已成为一个战略性的监管关切。'),
