  ('14facacb-88a6-4e41-b300-fa4792716fd0-ex1', '14facacb-88a6-4e41-b300-fa4792716fd0', 'illegal', 'Parking here is illegal.', '在这里停车是违法的。'),
  ('14facacb-88a6-4e41-b300-fa4792716fd0-ex2', '14facacb-88a6-4e41-b300-fa4792716fd0', 'illegal', 'The tribunal declared the expropriation illegal and ordered full reparation.', '法庭宣告这次征收非法，并责令全额赔偿。'),
