  ('b1954062-f766-4e35-8902-aca541ec2b24-ex1', 'b1954062-f766-4e35-8902-aca541ec2b24', 'personality', 'She has a warm personality.', '她性格温暖。'),
  ('b1954062-f766-4e35-8902-aca541ec2b24-ex2', 'b1954062-f766-4e35-8902-aca541ec2b24', 'personality', 'The cult of personality eroded the institutional checks the constitution envisaged.', '个人崇拜侵蚀了宪法所设想的制度制衡。'),
  ('c3a18620-0caf-40ac-924c-393104d16a9b-ex1', 'c3a18620-0caf-40ac-924c-393104d16a9b', 'signal', 'Wait for the green signal to cross.', '等绿灯亮了再过马路。'),
  ('c3a18620-0caf-40ac-924c-393104d16a9b-ex2', 'c3a18620-0caf-40ac-924c-393104d16a9b', 'signal', 'The rate decision was read as a signal of prolonged monetary accommodation.', '这次利率决定被解读为货币宽松将长期持续的信号。'),
  ('e478c6ba-e5ea-480d-9f9c-1f5383ea0e51-ex1', 'e478c6ba-e5ea-480d-9f9c-1f5383ea0e51', 'curriculum', 'The school updated its science curriculum.', '学校更新了科学课程。'),
  ('e478c6ba-e5ea-480d-9f9c-1f5383ea0e51-ex2', 'e478c6ba-e5ea-480d-9f9c-1f5383ea0e51', 'curriculum', 'The national curriculum embeds critical literacy across every subject area.', '国家课程将批判性素养融入每一个学科领域。'),
  ('05613b38-d90b-46ce-a1fc-7a4b69dc82e5-ex1', '05613b38-d90b-46ce-a1fc-7a4b69dc82e5', 'honor', 'It is an honor to meet you.', '见到您很荣幸。'),
  ('05613b38-d90b-46ce-a1fc-7a4b69dc82e5-ex2', '05613b38-d90b-46ce-a1fc-7a4b69dc82e5', 'honor', 'The state must honor obligations contracted by its predecessor governments.', '国家必须履行前任政府缔结的义务。'),
  ('4cc5b8ee-5518-43e6-a26c-5f80bab20c5c-ex1', '4cc5b8ee-5518-43e6-a26c-5f80bab20c5c', 'passenger', 'The bus can carry forty passengers.', '这辆公交车可载四十名乘客。'),
  ('4cc5b8ee-5518-43e6-a26c-5f80bab20c5c-ex2', '4cc5b8ee-5518-43e6-a26c-5f80bab20c5c', 'passenger', 'The convention codifies passenger rights to compensation for extended delays.', '该公约确立了乘客因长时间延误获得赔偿的权利。'),
  ('dded8dde-2fee-446d-8400-08b002880745-ex1', 'dded8dde-2fee-446d-8400-08b002880745', 'assistance', 'Do you need any assistance?', '您需要帮助吗？'),
  ('dded8dde-2fee-446d-8400-08b002880745-ex2', 'dded8dde-2fee-446d-8400-08b002880745', 'assistance', 'Mutual legal assistance treaties expedite evidence-sharing across borders.', '司法协助条约加快了跨境证据共享。'),
  ('451c09be-982e-4aab-b4f9-03bf9ff110c7-ex1', '451c09be-982e-4aab-b4f9-03bf9ff110c7', 'forever', 'I will remember this day forever.', '我会永远记住这一天。'),
  ('451c09be-982e-4aab-b4f9-03bf9ff110c7-ex2', '451c09be-982e-4aab-b4f9-03bf9ff110c7', 'forever', 'The ruling forever forecloses reliance on the contested exemption.', '该裁决永久排除了对争议豁免条款的援用。'),
  ('2a80c1da-7204-4d93-b1b5-aeeec438cc9b-ex1', '2a80c1da-7204-4d93-b1b5-aeeec438cc9b', 'regard', 'I have great regard for my teacher.', '我非常敬重我的老师。'),
  ('2a80c1da-7204-4d93-b1b5-aeeec438cc9b-ex2', '2a80c1da-7204-4d93-b1b5-aeeec438cc9b', 'regard', 'The parties differ sharply with regard to the allocation of consequential losses.', '双方在间接损失的分配问题上分歧严重。'),
  ('e77b2be2-6c9c-4971-a211-f38348d970f8-ex1', 'e77b2be2-6c9c-4971-a211-f38348d970f8', 'Israeli', 'We met an Israeli student at the conference.', '我们在会议上认识了一位以色列学生。'),
  ('e77b2be2-6c9c-4971-a211-f38348d970f8-ex2', 'e77b2be2-6c9c-4971-a211-f38348d970f8', 'Israeli', 'Israeli negotiators conditioned the framework on enforceable security guarantees.', '以色列谈判代表将该框架的达成系于可执行的安全保证。'),
  ('68963d60-601e-40c5-9e54-06bfcc9950ed-ex1', '68963d60-601e-40c5-9e54-06bfcc9950ed', 'association', 'She joined the parents'' association.', '她加入了家长协会。'),
  ('68963d60-601e-40c5-9e54-06bfcc9950ed-ex2', '68963d60-601e-40c5-9e54-06bfcc9950ed', 'association', 'The trade association lobbied vigorously against the disclosure mandates.', '行业协会对强制披露要求进行了大力游说抵制。'),
  ('96567e9b-93c8-4713-81a4-9e7d1f43ca80-ex1', '96567e9b-93c8-4713-81a4-9e7d1f43ca80', 'twenty', 'The bus leaves in twenty minutes.', '公交车二十分钟后出发。'),
  ('96567e9b-93c8-4713-81a4-9e7d1f43ca80-ex2', '96567e9b-93c8-4713-81a4-9e7d1f43ca80', 'twenty', 'The bonds mature in twenty years with coupons indexed to inflation.', '这些债券二十年后到期，票息与通胀挂钩。'),
  ('d83475d3-95e2-4733-8432-d160b7290131-ex1', 'd83475d3-95e2-4733-8432-d160b7290131', 'knock', 'Please knock before entering.', '进门前请敲门。'),
  ('d83475d3-95e2-4733-8432-d160b7290131-ex2', 'd83475d3-95e2-4733-8432-d160b7290131', 'knock', 'The tariff escalation delivered a serious knock to export-dependent manufacturers.', '关税升级对依赖出口的制造商造成了沉重打击。'),
