  ('f98535ac-7139-4063-b741-803833b0021e-ex1', 'f98535ac-7139-4063-b741-803833b0021e', 'lab', 'We did the experiment in the lab.', '我们在实验室做了实验。'),
  ('f98535ac-7139-4063-b741-803833b0021e-ex2', 'f98535ac-7139-4063-b741-803833b0021e', 'lab', 'Only accredited labs may perform the confirmatory assays the regulation requires.', '只有经认可的实验室才能进行法规要求的确证检测。'),
  ('8fd0f66f-5b08-4e32-a4b9-b69e905ceb22-ex1', '8fd0f66f-5b08-4e32-a4b9-b69e905ceb22', 'display', 'The museum displays ancient pottery.', '博物馆展出古代陶器。'),
  ('8fd0f66f-5b08-4e32-a4b9-b69e905ceb22-ex2', '8fd0f66f-5b08-4e32-a4b9-b69e905ceb22', 'display', 'Mandatory labels must display the verified energy rating of each appliance.', '强制性标签必须展示每件电器经核实的能效等级。'),
  ('6c852471-de55-4528-b238-8f217211b319-ex1', '6c852471-de55-4528-b238-8f217211b319', 'criticism', 'She accepted the criticism gracefully.', '她大度地接受了批评。'),
  ('6c852471-de55-4528-b238-8f217211b319-ex2', '6c852471-de55-4528-b238-8f217211b319', 'criticism', 'The framework drew criticism for delegating enforcement to private auditors.', '该框架因将执法委托给私营审计机构而受到批评。'),
  ('63f535f3-ba06-4ebe-b861-5ba834d741b9-ex1', '63f535f3-ba06-4ebe-b861-5ba834d741b9', 'asset', 'Her language skills are a real asset.', '她的语言能力是一大优势。'),
  ('63f535f3-ba06-4ebe-b861-5ba834d741b9-ex2', '63f535f3-ba06-4ebe-b861-5ba834d741b9', 'asset', 'The frozen assets may be released only under judicially supervised conditions.', '被冻结的资产只能在司法监督的条件下解冻。'),
  ('ed725d68-a8d7-4ec0-9ef2-04f780aafaed-ex1', 'ed725d68-a8d7-4ec0-9ef2-04f780aafaed', 'depression', 'Exercise can help with mild depression.', '锻炼有助于缓解轻度抑郁。'),
  ('ed725d68-a8d7-4ec0-9ef2-04f780aafaed-ex2', 'ed725d68-a8d7-4ec0-9ef2-04f780aafaed', 'depression', 'The depression of the 1930s reshaped assumptions about state economic intervention.', '二十世纪三十年代的大萧条重塑了人们对国家经济干预的认识。'),
  ('78e822fe-a75a-4aa2-8e78-5d3a1e8678e9-ex1', '78e822fe-a75a-4aa2-8e78-5d3a1e8678e9', 'spiritual', 'Music is a spiritual experience for her.', '对她来说，音乐是一种心灵体验。'),
  ('78e822fe-a75a-4aa2-8e78-5d3a1e8678e9-ex2', '78e822fe-a75a-4aa2-8e78-5d3a1e8678e9', 'spiritual', 'The site''s spiritual significance was weighed in the heritage determination.', '该遗址的精神意义在遗产认定中得到了考量。'),
  ('bf3f3dcf-201d-46bb-b8df-cc6b59c2ea62-ex1', 'bf3f3dcf-201d-46bb-b8df-cc6b59c2ea62', 'musical', 'We watched a musical last night.', '我们昨晚看了一场音乐剧。'),
  ('bf3f3dcf-201d-46bb-b8df-cc6b59c2ea62-ex2', 'bf3f3dcf-201d-46bb-b8df-cc6b59c2ea62', 'musical', 'The musical archive was digitized under a cross-border preservation accord.', '这批音乐档案根据跨境保护协议完成了数字化。'),
  ('635d38be-e17c-4ba8-9f5c-3bbb49bf442f-ex1', '635d38be-e17c-4ba8-9f5c-3bbb49bf442f', 'journalist', 'The journalist interviewed the mayor.', '记者采访了市长。'),
