  ('451b7dec-c6ef-4f27-bcae-995097bb51a2-ex1', '451b7dec-c6ef-4f27-bcae-995097bb51a2', 'prayer', 'They said a prayer before dinner.', '他们饭前做了祷告。'),
  ('451b7dec-c6ef-4f27-bcae-995097bb51a2-ex2', '451b7dec-c6ef-4f27-bcae-995097bb51a2', 'prayer', 'The ruling addressed the constitutionality of prayer in publicly funded schools.', '该裁决处理了公立学校祷告活动的合宪性问题。'),
