  ('d44b08d0-6eb4-499a-b91a-b4535214ba9c-ex1', 'd44b08d0-6eb4-499a-b91a-b4535214ba9c', 'climate', 'The climate here is mild all year.', '这里全年气候温和。'),
  ('d44b08d0-6eb4-499a-b91a-b4535214ba9c-ex2', 'd44b08d0-6eb4-499a-b91a-b4535214ba9c', 'climate', 'Climate litigation increasingly tests the boundaries of established tort doctrine.', '气候诉讼正日益挑战传统侵权法理论的边界。'),
