  ('4ad82565-4f7c-4a9f-b60d-c65484a1bc30-ex1', '4ad82565-4f7c-4a9f-b60d-c65484a1bc30', 'payment', 'The payment is due at the end of the month.', '付款月底到期。'),
  ('4ad82565-4f7c-4a9f-b60d-c65484a1bc30-ex2', '4ad82565-4f7c-4a9f-b60d-c65484a1bc30', 'payment', 'The facilitation payments at issue constitute bribery under the convention.', '涉案的疏通费按公约规定构成贿赂。'),
  ('fe12815d-f52b-4203-b980-ef4b1c285688-ex1', 'fe12815d-f52b-4203-b980-ef4b1c285688', 'sir', 'Excuse me, sir, you dropped your wallet.', '先生，打扰一下，您的钱包掉了。'),
