  ('fdc84334-5b7b-4d71-8900-4428c565c3cf-ex1', 'fdc84334-5b7b-4d71-8900-4428c565c3cf', 'cigarette', 'He quit smoking cigarettes last year.', '他去年戒了烟。'),
  ('fdc84334-5b7b-4d71-8900-4428c565c3cf-ex2', 'fdc84334-5b7b-4d71-8900-4428c565c3cf', 'cigarette', 'Plain packaging rules apply to every cigarette product sold domestically.', '平装规定适用于国内销售的所有香烟产品。'),
  ('0dfc3e6c-547c-4bc3-8f82-28ffe1026456-ex1', '0dfc3e6c-547c-4bc3-8f82-28ffe1026456', 'definition', 'Look up the definition in a dictionary.', '在字典里查一下定义。'),
  ('0dfc3e6c-547c-4bc3-8f82-28ffe1026456-ex2', '0dfc3e6c-547c-4bc3-8f82-28ffe1026456', 'definition', 'The statutory definition determines which entities fall within the licensing regime.', '法定定义决定了哪些实体属于许可制度的范围。'),
  ('11628111-e080-44e5-bd61-10bc392a9a66-ex1', '11628111-e080-44e5-bd61-10bc392a9a66', 'priority', 'My family is my first priority.', '家人是我的头等大事。'),
  ('11628111-e080-44e5-bd61-10bc392a9a66-ex2', '11628111-e080-44e5-bd61-10bc392a9a66', 'priority', 'Secured creditors enjoy priority over unsecured claims in insolvency distribution.', '在破产分配中，有担保债权人优先于无担保债权受偿。'),
  ('fbfa413a-4e03-46ec-99a8-5dedc496b916-ex1', 'fbfa413a-4e03-46ec-99a8-5dedc496b916', 'bread', 'The bakery sells fresh bread daily.', '这家面包店每天出售新鲜面包。'),
  ('fbfa413a-4e03-46ec-99a8-5dedc496b916-ex2', 'fbfa413a-4e03-46ec-99a8-5dedc496b916', 'bread', 'Subsidized bread prices anchored the social compact for a generation.', '面包补贴价格在一代人时间里维系着社会契约。'),
  ('4aa6b4d1-ea2e-49aa-a7e9-f4527010b0dc-ex1', '4aa6b4d1-ea2e-49aa-a7e9-f4527010b0dc', 'creation', 'The park''s creation took five years.', '这座公园的建设花了五年时间。'),
  ('4aa6b4d1-ea2e-49aa-a7e9-f4527010b0dc-ex2', '4aa6b4d1-ea2e-49aa-a7e9-f4527010b0dc', 'creation', 'The creation of the tribunal required amendment of the founding charter.', '设立该法庭需要修改创始章程。'),
  ('99b0e05f-c499-45a9-b504-c096a6bdd60c-ex1', '99b0e05f-c499-45a9-b504-c096a6bdd60c', 'graduate', 'She will graduate from college next year.', '她明年大学毕业。'),
  ('99b0e05f-c499-45a9-b504-c096a6bdd60c-ex2', '99b0e05f-c499-45a9-b504-c096a6bdd60c', 'graduate', 'Graduate retention has become a decisive metric in regional development policy.', '毕业生留存率已成为区域发展政策的关键指标。'),
  ('2297b51e-f6a1-4dc9-97a6-ccc57b2243f3-ex1', '2297b51e-f6a1-4dc9-97a6-ccc57b2243f3', 'request', 'I have a small request to make.', '我有个小请求。'),
  ('2297b51e-f6a1-4dc9-97a6-ccc57b2243f3-ex2', '2297b51e-f6a1-4dc9-97a6-ccc57b2243f3', 'request', 'The extradition request was refused on grounds of potential political persecution.', '该引渡请求因可能存在政治迫害而被拒绝。'),
  ('9510277f-a2ca-43e7-8b34-0af10177761a-ex1', '9510277f-a2ca-43e7-8b34-0af10177761a', 'emotion', 'Her voice was full of emotion.', '她的声音充满感情。'),
  ('9510277f-a2ca-43e7-8b34-0af10177761a-ex2', '9510277f-a2ca-43e7-8b34-0af10177761a', 'emotion', 'The proceedings demand dispassionate analysis uncolored by public emotion.', '这些诉讼需要不受公众情绪影响的冷静分析。'),
  ('7f1f6345-29c5-4219-a9de-51f9dbaba157-ex1', '7f1f6345-29c5-4219-a9de-51f9dbaba157', 'scream', 'We heard a scream from the street.', '我们听到街上传来一声尖叫。'),
  ('7f1f6345-29c5-4219-a9de-51f9dbaba157-ex2', '7f1f6345-29c5-4219-a9de-51f9dbaba157', 'scream', 'The headlines screamed of betrayal while the legal substance remained unexamined.', '新闻标题高喊背叛，法律实质却无人深究。'),
  ('c3ab538b-612d-4b67-84df-b1960c53a632-ex1', 'c3ab538b-612d-4b67-84df-b1960c53a632', 'dramatic', 'The game had a dramatic ending.', '比赛的结局充满戏剧性。'),
  ('c3ab538b-612d-4b67-84df-b1960c53a632-ex2', 'c3ab538b-612d-4b67-84df-b1960c53a632', 'dramatic', 'The disclosure produced a dramatic repricing of the issuer''s entire debt stack.', '这一披露使发行人的整体债务结构出现剧烈重新定价。'),
  ('de563c6d-1a6c-4315-a2ff-b2c50a7da903-ex1', 'de563c6d-1a6c-4315-a2ff-b2c50a7da903', 'universe', 'The universe is full of stars.', '宇宙中布满星辰。'),
